<div class="rounded-lg m-5 p-5 text-center bg-pink-white relative">
  <p class="text-xl text-matte font-bold mb-2"><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i>質問に答えて、自分を見つけてみませんか？</p>
  <div class="rounded-lg py-3 mb-3 text-matte bg-white shadow-inner relative">
    <%= link_to new_diary_path(title: write.title) do %>
      <div class="text-2xl flex justify-center hover:opacity-75">
        <i class="fas fa-check mr-5"></i>
        <p class="text-xl lg:text-md text-matte font-thin items-center"><%= write.title %></p>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <%= link_to root_path do %>
    <div class="text-3xl rounded-full h-12 w-12 flex items-center justify-center text-white bg-amber absolute right-1 bottom-0.5 shadow-inner">
      <i class="fas fa-random"></i>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  <p class="text-right text-sm lg:text-xs text-matte font-thin mt-4 mr-10"><i class="fas fa-random"></i>マークをクリックまたはタッチすることで質問が変わります。</p>
</div>
